16 SECTION 2. A new section to chapter 50-24.5 of the North Dakota Century Code is created
17 and enacted as follows:
18 Adult residential facility payment rates - Report .
19 1. The department shall increase rates for inflation for the year beginning:
20 a. July 1, 2025, by four percent; and
21 b. July 1, 2026, by three percent .
22 2. The department shall require an adult residential facility to submit cost reports and
23 supplemental information by October 31, 2025, which the department shall use to pay
24 the facility its current costs beginning January 1, 2026 .
25 3. Beginning January 1, 2026, a five percent operating margin must be included in adul t
26 residential facility rates.
27 4. The department shall require adult residential facilities to submit cost reports and
28 supplemental information by December 31, 2026, which the department shall use to
29 provide a rate recalculation beginning July 1, 2027 .
